{
  "stem": "16214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Worked about seven hours after the first month or so of being in school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then I went to school for six hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So it was a very, very difficult time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the thing is that I was very inquisitive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I always wanted to be a doctor, not a nurse, and do research.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And basically, most of the doctors, if you ask them questions there, they would just say to you, you know, mind your own business type of thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean they never wanted to really explain to you anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and I just wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this sort of thing did not agree with me very well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I was very angry at both of my parents for sort of, instead of sending me to regular high school, to finish the high school, because I had two years of Polish high school, you know, to be sent off to nursing school.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because this is the thing that you could do after two years of high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You could go to that nursing school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they basically run my life for me, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I was starting to rebel against it, as a teenager too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So when they had the documents prepared that they're going to go to the United States, all my friends, all my cousins would say, now they send you here to nursing school.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You don't like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Probably if you go to the United States, they will send you to factory to work, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Which of course, was not true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was totally nonsense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But in my mind, you know, it was like I don't want to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I like it here now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I'm going to stay here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But I definitely am not going to stay in nursing school.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
